data.description: *Offer has been accepted. Property is staying active through the inspection period for back up offers.* Located in InvestDSM’s Special Investment District.  If you love the warmth and charm of turn of the century architecture, don’t miss this beautifully restored 1912 Wessex gem. Here you’ll find 3 floors of living space starting with a charming enclosed front porch, drop zone, large living room with brand new gas fireplace, den with large bay window, half bath, dining room with original built ins, updated kitchen, mud room, and enclosed back porch. The second floor features 4 bedrooms, a sun-drenched solarium overlooking the deep backyard and a full bath with jet tub. The third floor is open the entire length of the home offering ample room for work or play or non-conforming bedroom. The dry lower level has  a newer HVAC system, another 3/4 bath, laundry and ample storage. Don’t miss out on this unique opportunity to make a remarkable example of 1910s craftsmanship and modern convenience your own.
